Overview
It’s the final chapter in the first arc of this top-selling title from the mind of Stephen King.
Roland and his ka-tet have their long-awaited showdown with Eldred Jonas and the Big Coffin Hunters. And on the outcome of this fateful confrontation rests the future of Mid-world itself!
Plus—the tragic conclusion of Roland Deschain’s love affair with Susan Delgado and much, much more!
